{"tid":1774320,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日需唔需要戴口罩？","createTime":"2019-12-08T07:42:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-08T08:00:28.000Z","uid":227650,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"463d70825192c1d9a670b66c748840dc11785435","tid":1774320,"uid":227650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T07:42:03.000Z","msg":"如題"},{"pid":"65139e1e3d91ef366e60032afbe5c111acb80c15","tid":1774320,"uid":761,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T07:42:30.000Z","msg":"Black bloc  <br />\n完"},{"pid":"f23ccef63c3dbb17322178114fc052fc78ea857a","tid":1774320,"uid":114487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T07:43:02.000Z","msg":"出黎先再諗"},{"pid":"af6c1a2f4b6368d40d90a40020603e36d4ffd1b0","tid":1774320,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T07:43:12.000Z","msg":"自己諗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"903401b74ff3cbf386b43165b8a65118e5663376","tid":1774320,"uid":321154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T07:44:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fcfe35c038efa6276a535e3bbc19966e97fa998","tid":1774320,"uid":226925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T07:45:48.000Z","msg":"禁蒙面法係咪暫緩到10號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 究極和理非諗緊戴唔戴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"426a39679c37dd8d0ffbce614c534acf0ea89f93","tid":1774320,"uid":20563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T07:46:15.000Z","msg":"立場報道2019/10/23 &mdash; 12:06<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港府近年設置「智慧燈柱」，被外界質疑設有人像識別功能，其中 8 月 24 日有示威者拆毀觀塘的「智慧燈柱」以作抗議，不少市民亦在示威中蒙面，以防警方追查。彭博（Bloomberg）今日最新報道指，香港警察一直使用總部位於澳洲悉尼的人工智能系統生產商 iOmniscient，該軟件可將任何錄像中的面孔與警察數據庫進行匹配，並從中挑選出疑犯。生產商則拒絕評論香港警察有否使用相關技術。<br />\n<br />\n彭博報道指，警方已使用有關技術至少三年，該公司已對本港數十多名警員進行培訓，但未知是否已應用過去四個月的示威活動。報道稱，該軟件同時可作尋找失蹤兒童，並引述知情人士指，生產商曾在六月初提供了一堂培訓，有警員詢問如何使用軟件自動識別車牌編號。<br />\n<br />\n生產商 iOmniscient 回覆彭博，拒絕評論香港警方是否使用有關技術，又指該軟件已在50多個國家及地區使用，總收入中只有小部分來自香港，又指由於香港隱私問題及攝錄機數量較其他國家少，因此香港的商機相對有限。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/彭博-香港警察採人像識別功能逾三年-所攝錄像可與警方數據庫匹配/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%BD%AD%E5%8D%9A-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E6%8E%A1%E4%BA%BA%E5%83%8F%E8%AD%98%E5%88%A5%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E9%80%BE%E4%B8%89%E5%B9%B4-%E6%89%80%E6%94%9D%E9%8C%84%E5%83%8F%E5%8F%AF%E8%88%87%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E5%BA%AB%E5%8C%B9%E9%85%8D%2F&d=u6uLjzzFZj4TH%2F5rj7Ekc6npKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=fa1ddee2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%BD%AD%E5%8D%9A-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E6%8E%A1%E4%BA%BA%E5%83%8F%E8%AD%98%E5%88%A5%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E9%80%BE%E4%B8%89%E5%B9%B4-%E6%89%80%E6%94%9D%E9%8C%84%E5%83%8F%E5%8F%AF%E8%88%87%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E5%BA%AB%E5%8C%B9%E9%85%8D%2F&h=951edf10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/彭博-香港警察採人像識別功能逾三年-所攝錄像可與警方數據庫匹配/</a>"},{"pid":"c50425a3819974c43dd033771e45cce53ea52dc7","tid":1774320,"uid":208689,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T07:50:47.000Z","msg":"盡量保護自己<br />\n先係對香港負責任"},{"pid":"5e38699e08feeea5bb8b930f11c91407b8f099c3","tid":1774320,"uid":227650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c50425a3819974c43dd033771e45cce53ea52dc7","tid":1774320,"uid":208689,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T07:50:47.000Z","msg":"盡量保護自己<br />\n先係對香港負責任"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T07:52:44.000Z","msg":"收到"},{"pid":"ad2d21896af4b633a3f6f9159ae980d074dfff4e","tid":1774320,"uid":155012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T07:53:23.000Z","msg":"幾時問埋洗唔洗飲水"},{"pid":"2fe5297ed9dc066568bbfd53fded281735b4a52d","tid":1774320,"uid":263618,"like":0,"dislike"